    <text>
        <body>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Charleston So Ca</placeName>
                <date>November 7. 5611</date>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">To</p>
            <p>The <addressee>Revd I Leeser</addressee></p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(4)">Worthy Sir!</p>
            <p>It was with deep regret, that I <sic>learnt</sic> and learn that
                    <placeName>Israel</placeName> is as ungrateful to their<lb/>
                <hi rend="underline">true</hi> Teachers and Prophets now as it was in the days of
                old. Whilst hypocrisy which calls<lb/> yet <add>שלום שלום ואין שלום</add> is raised
                to the pinnacles of Wealth and to honor bordering on adoration.<lb/> Your friends
                here, which you well know are numerous, regret deeply the loss of your<lb/>
                Congregation, and your disappointment. Worthy Sir! I beg leave to send you the
                following<lb/> communications, which may be worthy of a place in your esteemed
                Occident. If so, you<lb/> will oblige</p>
            <p rend="indent(5)">your devoted</p>
            <p rend="indent(6)">
                <persName role="author">J. Eckman</persName>
            </p>
            <p>I allow you or beg you if required to insert them with your<lb/> editorial remarks,
                as for the 2d you may alter the Phraseology<lb/> if you think proper and being
                written in haste to alter,<lb/> as to the name you may give it as there can be no
                objection<lb/> If there should be any charges I will remit it by <persName>Mr
                    Hart</persName><lb/> from this place</p>
        </body>
